Musk-deer (
<taxonomicName id="4C6F28C5FFB8F05EF86DF2851128F29E" box="[2012,2113,3395,3415]" class="Mammalia" family="Moschidae" genus="Moschus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="2" pageNumber="345" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Moschus</taxonomicName>
ınhuıensısl, 7 Forest Musk-deer (
<taxonomicName id="4C6F28C5FFB8F05EFFC9F2AC1835F2B7" box="[120,348,3434,3454]" class="Mammalia" family="Moschidae" genus="Moschus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="2" pageNumber="345" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="berezovskii">Moschus berezovskıı</taxonomicName>
